# निवेश-निर्गम — I/O helpers. Effects are pure data: मुद्रण (print), पठन (read),
# शुद्ध (pure), and बन्ध (bind) are constructors the runtime interprets. The only
# thing to define here is sequencing.

अधिकार निवेश।

# अनुक्रम — run ?अ, ignore its result, then run ?ब. (The `>>` operator.)
सूत्र अनुक्रम(?अ, ?ब) -> बन्ध(?अ, (?अव) => ?ब)।
